  20 Mar 2016; Andreas K. Hüttel <dilfridge@gentoo.org>
  vmware-workstation-11.1.3.3206955-r3.ebuild,
  vmware-workstation-11.1.3.3206955-r4.ebuild,
  vmware-workstation-12.1.0.3272444-r2.ebuild:
  remove RESTRICT=preserve-libs, makes no sense

  This restrict means that libraries from *this* package are not preserved.
  We have the exact opposite problem, we want that this package does not
  *cause*
  other libraries to be preserved...

